Package org.aserg.model

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Auth
    Singleton for representing an authentication attempt in SshIncident.
    Incident
    This is the main incident class which contains all the common elements found in all its subtypes.
    Input
    Singleton for representing the commands executed by attacker in SshIncident.
    MalwareIncident
    This class represents the Incident where a malware has been downloaded by the attacker.
    MssqlIncident
    This class represents the Incident that where the attacker attempts to exploit the vulnerabilities emulated in the MSSQL service.
    MysqlCommand
    Singleton for storing MySQL commands for MysqlIncident.
    MysqlIncident
    This class represents the Incident where the attacker exploited exposed vulnerabilities of the MySQL service.
    NetworkLayerIncident
    Network Layer Incident where snort alert is triggered.
    Origin
    Information about the origin of the attack, and its geolocation information.
    SipIncident
    This class represents the Incident that employs the VoIP Session Initiation Protocol.
    SshIncident
    This class represents an SSH Incident.
    VirusTotalScan
    This class contains the virustotal scan reference and individual scanner results.
    WebIncident
    This class represents an Incident on the Application Layer.
    WebRule
    Singleton for describing the Modsecurity rule triggered by the WebIncident.
